<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hit-n">hit <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /hɪt/    美 /hɪt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>打击；击中；(对网站的) 点击：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our ship took a <strong>direct hit</strong> and sank.
我们的船被直接击中下沉了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The website gets 100,000 hits every day.
每日该网站的点击次数为10万次。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>风行一时的作品；轰动一时的成功人物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an Internet hit
网红</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When he first arrived in the US, Yao was an instant hit among basketball fans nationwide.
初到美国，姚明就在全美的篮球爱好者中一夜成名。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="take-a-hit">take a hit</h3>
<p>1.<strong>遭到破坏；受到严重影响</strong>  </p></div>